comment._content:
I believe this submarine is one of the six "J" class submarines which were a gift of the British Admiralty to the Royal Australian Navy.  

Seen here being refitted, not actually constructed.

I'll try to narrow it down.

{comment edited, changing number of J-class subs in the gift from five to the correct six}
